race.comment: SPEEDY SCRUB (1) has an impeccable record this course and distance, winning all three starts. Comes off a (21.56) win last time, scoring by 2.5 lengths in a OPEN over 390m at this track. Has the ability and should feature. HOPE'S ZONE (2) is a progressive type who recorded her 36th career win last time out (21.60) at this track. Solid record here at the distance winning four races. Has a strong record out of this box with four wins and a minor placing from eight starts. Bold showing expected again. HARA'S NEO (5) is a talented type and proved too classy last time to win by 3 lengths at this track in a handy 21.52 beating PERKY PENNY. Ran the fastest time on the program in her latest win. Likely to be in the finish. PERKY PENNY (8) hit the frame latest (21.73) when second at this track in a OPEN. Has already won four times from this draw.
